<header class="artic-word-header">
    <p class="artic-word-title"><i class="fas fa-tasks"></i> ITSM Personal Todo</p>
</header>
<div class="artic-word-scroll-indicator"></div>
<main class="artic-word-main">
    <h2 class="artic-word-heading">Personal ITSM Todo Interface Function Overview. </h2>
    <p>To improve efficiency in IT Service Management (ITSM) workflows for individual users, a lightweight Todo creation interface has been developed. It is mainly used for recording and managing personal tasks, allowing users to easily add, view, follow up, and set reminders. The interface focuses on quick creation and simple operation, suitable for daily operations, development, or request tracking.</p>
    <hr>
    <h3>To-do List</h3>
    <p>All created tasks are displayed on the main page in a list format, with the following features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Filter by status: All / Doing / Completed</li>
        <li>Sort by number: Arrange tasks by task number in ascending or descending order</li>
        <li>Delete tasks: Select tasks and click the Delete button to remove them</li>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <h3>Task Creation</h3>
    <p>Creating a task is straightforward:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Title is a required field</li>
        <li>After entering the title, click the Create button in the top-right corner to add the task</li>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <h3>Support & Feedback</h3>
    <p>If you encounter any issues with the Todo interface, please contact the IT department for assistance.</p>
</main>
